{"tid":784283,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★港樓爆？Buyers flee Hong Kong property as credit crunch bites","createTime":"2018-08-18T08:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T19:33:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"91b7c7c2150c156160f50f89a93a5ee4030394a4","tid":784283,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong&rsquo;s housing boom is starting to fray as monetary tightening by the US Federal Reserve forces the enclave&rsquo;s authorities to tighten credit.<br />\n<br />\nA rash of home buyers has pulled out of purchases at the last moment despite losing large deposits, a sign that financial stress is biting harder or that fear is creeping into the market.<br />\n<br />\nThe South China Morning Post said buyers had pulled out of five flats in Sun Hung Kai&rsquo;s Park Yoho Milano complex this week, losing $250,000 in US dollars between them. Another cancelled at the Sun Hung Kai Properties Martin II, losing $46,000; a further pulled out of the Zumurud development, losing $250,000. One developer is cutting prices by 10pc to clear inventory...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2018/08/17/buyers-flee-hong-kong-property-credit-crunch-bites/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fbusiness%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2Fbuyers-flee-hong-kong-property-credit-crunch-bites%2F&d=C81KD9EBn27IKq%2FxOCqikJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5fc62415\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2018/08/17/buyers-flee-hong-kong-property-credit-crunch-bites/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ngoogle翻譯：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">買家因信貸危機而逃離香港房地產</span><br />\n<br />\n隨著美國聯邦儲備委員會收緊貨幣政策迫使飛地當局收緊信貸，香港房地產市場的繁榮開始動搖。<br />\n<br />\n儘管失去了大量存款，一連串的購房者已經在最後時刻退出購買，這表明金融壓力更加刺激，或者恐懼正在蔓延到市場。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;南華早報&rdquo;本週表示買家已經在新鴻基公園Yoho Milano綜合體中退出了五個單位，兩者之間損失了25萬美元。 另一位在新鴻基地產馬丁二世取消，損失46,000美元; 進一步退出了Zumurud的開發，損失了25萬美元。 一位開發商將價格降低10個百分點以清理庫存......"},{"pid":"fcf86fb5ec351830628f51a5dda44880bb5347ba","tid":784283,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f7cc0d9138bf5b4d683a256ab2880459ac6f48","tid":784283,"uid":29080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/011320_10aa9daa7e7a280c1087ef038496576e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F011320_10aa9daa7e7a280c1087ef038496576e.gif&h=325a6fbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5b8948f1c87e42bacde8625af25c50c2b783cf1","tid":784283,"uid":31773,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"樓價gogogo<br />\n<br />\n港樓點會跌，剛需咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14aa4ff173ac9119568bac7322cf2d26b67e93c6","tid":784283,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"Low more<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bdff9ace97f06e4dae12f6c4d4fb52b5d62af9","tid":784283,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"Y U here <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4007cc2fb02cb73f657975967da14ec857915de8","tid":784283,"uid":19454,"like"